  "name": "Generate invoice pdf from QuickBooks transaction and send to Google Drive",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from ritik-prog/n8n-automation-templates-5000: Generate invoice pdf from QuickBooks transaction and send to Google Drive",
  "category": "Communication",
